CITATION: 1986 AIR 1518 1986 SCR (2) 59 1986 SCC (2) 608 1986 SCALE (1)500 
ACT:
 Bombay Municipal Boroughs Act, 1925, section 77, scope of - Whether the rules for the levy of a rate on buildings and lands can be said to be published under section 77 of the Act, if the notice published in a newspaper reciting the sanction of the State Government to the rules mentions that the rules themselves are open to inspection in the Municipal office and that copies of the rules can also be purchased there.
 
